These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: card-games, collecting
House: palace, townhouse
1. House:palace is in an even position##4
2. House:townhouse == Hobby:collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| House     | townhouse    | palace   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Birthday: may, august
Sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:august is on the left of Birthday:may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Birthday   | august | may        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Food: lemon, grapes
Nationality: canadian, turkish
1. Nationality:canadian is in an odd position##4
2. Food:grapes is on the left of Food:lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Food   | grapes    | lemon |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
Pet: snake, bird
